{"tid":1201680,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(有圖）岩岩發現愛廸生真係偉大科學家","createTime":"2019-06-11T05:55:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T06:02:24.000Z","uid":218090,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"05559f585a8aa51b2baad70e13c77206e1de71ae","tid":1201680,"uid":218090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T05:55:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/爱迪生\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-tw%2F%E7%88%B1%E8%BF%AA%E7%94%9F&d=0xAgwAOhMzbM3o1MPcLVDwy7VxIBYRqzliHj24KwcnI%3D&h=a43821b9\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/爱迪生</a><br />\n<br />\n愛迪生發明了很多東西，包括：對世界極大影響的留聲機、電燈、活動電影攝影機、直流電力系統等最為人知。在美國，愛迪生名下擁有1093項專利，而他在美國、英國、法國和德國等地的專利數累計超過150項[2]。他一生最偉大的兩項專利一項為留聲機，它可以保留並播放聲音， 另外一項專利倍受爭議，那就是世人所熟知的電燈，通過六年的漫長法庭鬥爭最後以愛迪生成功獲得專利告終。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QsyBiUf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQsyBiUf.png&h=a16d1f93&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"060a328f7ac174712dbefe0ccf2e9e9126770717","tid":1201680,"uid":218090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T05:57:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/06/11/135725_e148fc804d356d872749eae91855d289.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F06%2F11%2F135725_e148fc804d356d872749eae91855d289.png&h=a7966f0a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"27d73408517d1c1a9e1dfd553b6d63202b5e0369","tid":1201680,"uid":82033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T05:59:17.000Z","msg":"喺高登讚愛sir係死罪"},{"pid":"de55a7afb86a565655e1bc798d27427e0ba2f0f7","tid":1201680,"uid":68689,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T05:59:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/d/d4/N.Tesla.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%